The use of weights in the grammars suggests a focus on discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL). The exploration of random generation techniques suggests a possible connection to computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the study of distributions induced by the grammars suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG).
